		(descr "XKB SK-3296S-01-L2 right-angle SMD SPDT slide switch; C500051. Manufacturer land pattern: 0.8x2.0mm signal pads, 1.4x0.8mm mounting pads on 7.3x2.2mm pitch, and two 0.9mm locator holes on 3.0mm pitch. Align the Dwgs.User line at Y=1.90mm with the PCB edge; this leaves 0.40mm clearance from the mounting pads and approximately 1.45mm actuator overhang.")
